headline: PDM Secures Over 500K Square Feet of Leases in Third Quarter to Date
summary: Piedmont secures more than 500K sq ft of leases in the third quarter to date, with strong tenant demand fueling occupancy and rental income growth.

headline: All You Need to Know About Crown Castle (CCI) Rating Upgrade to Buy
summary: Crown Castle (CCI) might move higher on growing optimism about its earnings prospects, which is reflected by its upgrade to a Zacks Rank #2 (Buy).

headline: How Is Crown Castle’s Stock Performance Compared to Other Real Estate Stocks?
summary: Crown Castle has lagged behind its industry peers over the past year, and Wall Street analysts maintain a reasonably upbeat view on its future growth potential.
